Follow the repository contract before editing.

- Read `AGENTS.md`, `ai/prompt-web-generator.md`, `content/raw.txt`, and `content/brief.yaml` before changing AI-generated website content.
- Treat `content/brief.yaml` as the primary structured source of truth for generated website content.
- Preserve the current Next.js App Router structure, reusable components, engines, routes, and responsive behavior.
- Do not redesign the whole site, delete components, or break layout balance.
- Keep hero and section titles concise, balanced, and within 2 lines on desktop and mobile.
- Subtitle copy may be wider than the title when needed for clarity.
- Reuse existing components and generate professional, conversion-focused copy.
